Spotify playlist:
https://open.spotify.com/user/jesiennik/playlist/0gbLmEN1EuRmg1cx709U3E

NEWS: 
As the songs keep pouring in our queue at a breakneck speed, we're raising the daily song limit for next week to 4 per day. It's a lot, I know, but otherwise some of you would have to wait until the 13th (!) to get their songs published :) 

Konrad destroyed us completely with his video puzzle last week, so this week we're going back to the good-old-and-too-easy riddles devised by moi ;)

As a bonus, you're getting a pic of an otter showing the followers what it means to be wonderfully lazy in their movements, not to rush and wait patiently for the leader's move ;) 
#nie_chce_mi_się

Enjoy!

Cheers from sunny Kraków!
Joanna 

P.S.: Don't forget to check out Ed Sheeran's new album! <3
